^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Over 2C Michaels cue bid there is an interesting convention available to me called "Unusual over Unusual" which usually applies after an unusual 2N because the two suits are usually known. It also applies after a Michaels cuebid when the two suits are known. In this case 2C by Vered shows spades and hearts exactly. Therefore, I have two additional bids available to me - 2H and 2S cuebids.|
