NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|If I make a cuebid in the lower suit (heart here) that shows a good hand with clubs. And if I cuebid the higher suit - spades here - I am showing a strong hand with diamonds. In either case, It should be obvious to the partner that my bids are artificial as Vered is showing both suits in one bid. Therefore with my hand the correct bid is 2S - good hand with diamonds. Both bids are alertable. If I was not play the "Unusal over Unusual" convention I would bid 2D which is forcing and shows diamonds.|
